{"tid":2515791,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港電台升旗禮 國歌唱完女童軍都扯唔到旗","createTime":"2021-05-04T08:24:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T11:46:47.000Z","uid":13745,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"21efee4c92e10c07bba418696a64a34800eab8b9","tid":2515791,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:24:40.000Z","msg":"高舉全面落實商經局檢討報告旗號也難掩政治魔爪的廣播處長李百全，自3月上任後除立法會外未有出席公開活動，至今早才首度公開現身港台五四運動升旗禮，卻對連番抽起節目、利君雅不獲續約等均沒有回應。升旗禮期間，國旗一度無法升起。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8時正式升旗時，由女童軍負責的中國國旗至國歌演奏畢，仍未能成功升旗。旁邊的香港區旗也因中國國旗未有成功升起。現場隨即有工作人員走到旗杆協助處理，再大叫指令升旗，終在沒有演奏國歌下，國旗和區旗成功升起。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/oB9P7MV-86kZ0HCHIu_FouAysr0=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BWWOKHP5PJDDXN4VC5OUQ3BB7Q.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FoB9P7MV-86kZ0HCHIu_FouAysr0%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBWWOKHP5PJDDXN4VC5OUQ3BB7Q.JPG&h=b6f78789&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f520027bffb3593794cddec0ab33b68ddbb84ba7","tid":2515791,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:29:41.000Z","msg":"邪撚到"},{"pid":"cc648b6407f427833fb645471e0a86013d01a72b","tid":2515791,"uid":3241,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:32:01.000Z","msg":"班小曱甴仲係用英式敬禮喎<br />\n屌你老母愛国唔係每人一條血紅綁狗式頸巾大叫忠党愛国咩"},{"pid":"68f5e77e5330ca81a8d1f23e0be614c7c893f9aa","tid":2515791,"uid":204539,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"女童軍勁淫蕩<br />\n條裙Form1著到Form 6<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae82bfdc3844c545d973255c50c23289142b3d3","tid":2515791,"uid":198245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:38:57.000Z","msg":"拉得啦，犯晒国安法"},{"pid":"9c690af2452e5d64d934685cd253192e5f01905d","tid":2515791,"uid